  Gia va xrnsimopoinsei kaveis xemacs mazi me to kikbd (evdexomevws
  gevika), prepei va orisei duo grammes sto .xemacs-options:

  (global-set-key 'Dacute_accent '"")
  (global-set-key 'Ddiaeresis '"")



